                               double requestDuration,
                               double timeToFirstByte,
                               double contentDownloadDuration)
Initializing constructor. All times are in seconds.

Parameters:
startTime - Trace time when request/response started
dnsLookupDuration - duration of DNS lookup or null if no DNS lookup
initialConnDuration - duration of session initiation or null if already initiated
sslNegotiationDuration - duration of SSL negotiation or null if N/A
requestDuration - duration of request upload
timeToFirstByte - wait time for response
contentDownloadDuration - duration of response download
